Skill: Counter     Timer: None         GL:  9    Cost: NONE

After a certain amount of combat experience, a fighter gains 
the knowledge of how to turn an attack back on its attacker.

This is not something that can be done often during the course
of a battle but is something that a fighter with the proper
skill level can do without thinking occasionally in the course
of battle.

Counter uses endurance when you counter-attack.

Syntax is: ftoggle counter <on|off>
